Template: bitmesh/outface
Type: select
Choices: ${choices}
Description: What interface has an internet connection?
 What interface is actively connected to the internet?
 If you have a wired connection to a router this is
 normally eth0.

Template: bitmesh/inface
Type: select
Choices: ${choices}
Description: What interface will clients be connecting to? 
 Clients will be using this interface to gain access to
 the internet. So if you have an internet connection on
 eth0, then this interface would most likely be wlan0.